Ingress -> Configure rules to map url -> host, path

Configures below service which helps to access a pod exposed service:

 * ClusterIP - sharing a pod service within the app so that other pods can access
 * NodePort - sharing a pod service external
 * LoadBalancer - sharing external with LoadBalancer like NGINX

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VicH6KojwCI
 
